---
import Button from '../Button.astro';
---
<div class="cost-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
<section class="cost-section" id="cost">
  <div class="cost-inner">
    <!-- Section label -->
    <p class="section-label">// 09 COST OF WAITING</p>

    <!-- Content wrapper - 640px -->
    <div class="cost-content">
      <!-- Headline -->
      <h2 class="cost-headline">
        <span>You're already paying for this.</span>
        <span>You just don't have an invoice for it yet.</span>
      </h2>

      <!-- Body copy -->
      <div class="cost-body">
        <p>
          That slow month. That competitor who keeps winning work you know you
          could do better. That referral who visited your site and never called
          back. There's no line item for any of it. But the cost is real and
          it's compounding.
        </p>

        <p>
          Every day you're copying and pasting between tools that weren't
          designed to work together, re-answering the same intake questions,
          rebuilding the same follow-up from scratch. That time is already gone.
        </p>

        <p>
          Word-of-mouth works until it stops. When it does, there's nothing
          underneath it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Terminal stat block -->
      <div class="cost-stats">
        <div class="stat-line">
          <span class="stat-label stat-danger">&gt; DAILY TIME LOST TO WASTED ADMIN (per owner):</span>
          <span class="stat-value stat-danger">~1.5 hrs</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-line">
          <span class="stat-label stat-danger">&gt; THAT'S PER WEEK:</span>
          <span class="stat-value stat-danger">~7.5 hrs</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-line">
          <span class="stat-label stat-danger">&gt; THAT'S PER YEAR:</span>
          <span class="stat-value stat-danger">~1 full work month</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-line">
          <span class="stat-label stat-danger">&gt; SOLOPRENEURS WHO'VE LOST A MONTH OF INCOME:</span>
          <span class="stat-value stat-danger">42%</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-line">
          <span class="stat-label stat-danger">&gt; SMALL BIZ OWNERS CONFIDENT THEIR MARKETING WORKS:</span>
          <span class="stat-value stat-danger">1 in 5</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-line stat-line-positive">
          <span class="stat-label stat-success">&gt; COST TO DIAGNOSE:</span>
          <span class="stat-value stat-success">$0.00</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-line">
          <span class="stat-label stat-compounding">&gt; COST TO DO NOTHING:</span>
          <span class="stat-value stat-compounding">compounding</span>
        </div>
        <p class="stat-source">// Slack / Salesforce, 2024 · Simply Business, 2025, n=1,023 · Constant Contact / Ascend2, 2025</p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="cost-cta">
        <Button variant="ghost" href="/diagnostic">[RUN THE FREE DIAGNOSTIC &gt;]</Button>
        <Button variant="primary" href="#diagnostic">[START YOUR PROJECT &gt;]</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Amber divider rule at top */
  .cost-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  /* Red-shifted dark background */
  .cost-section {
    background: var(--bg-cost-waiting);
    color: var(--text);
    padding: var(--space-24) var(--space-8);
  }

  .cost-inner {
    max-width: var(--container-xl);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* Section label */
  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  /* Content wrapper - 640px */
  .cost-content {
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  /* Headline */
  .cost-headline {
    font-family: var(--font-pixel);
    font-size: var(--step-4);
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .cost-headline span {
    display: block;
  }

  .cost-headline span:first-child {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .cost-headline span:last-child {
    color: oklch(0.76 0.18 62 / 0.7);
  }

  /* Body copy */
  .cost-body {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .cost-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: oklch(0.88 0.06 62);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .cost-body p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Terminal stat block */
  .cost-stats {
    background: var(--crt-black);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-feature-settings: 'tnum' 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-12);
  }

  .stat-line {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-1) 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .stat-line-positive {
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .stat-value {
    font-size: var(--step--2);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-align: right;
  }

  .stat-danger {
    color: var(--danger);
  }

  .stat-success {
    color: var(--success);
  }

  .stat-compounding {
    color: var(--amber-4);
  }

  .stat-source {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-accent-dim);
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    padding-top: var(--space-3);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* CTA area */
  .cost-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .cost-section {
      padding: var(--space-16) var(--space-6);
    }

    .cost-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-3);
    }

    .stat-line {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: var(--space-1);
    }

    .stat-value {
      text-align: left;
    }

    .cost-cta {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .cost-headline {
      font-size: var(--step-2);
    }
  }
</style>
